        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The carved night hag's hand at the end of this sandalwood staff clutches a rough gem. The <em>Staff of the Dreamlands</em> makes it easier to navigate and survive in the Dreamlands and recognize its denizens. When wielding the staff, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Survival checks while in the Dreamlands and to checks to Recall Knowledge about creatures with the dream trait.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Cast a Spell]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Daze]</li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Alarm], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Déjà Vu], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sleep]</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Phantasmal Treasure], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Silence]</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
